Install OSM Plugin
→ Plugins → Manage and Install Plugins → Install OpenStreetMap Plugin

Add OpenStreetMap Layer
→ Web → OpenLayer Plugin → OpenStreetMap → OpenStreetMap

Set Project CRS
→ Project → Properties → CRS → EPSG: 3857

Enable OSM Place Search Panel
→ View → Panels → OSM Place Search
→ Search "Gateway of India" (18.92°N, 72.83°E)

Open Georeferencer
→ Raster → Georeferencer
→ File → Open Raster
→ Select Gateway_Imagery.tif

Add Control Points
→ Edit → Add Point
→ Select points from the map (red marks)

Start Georeferencing
→ File → Start Georeferencing
